1
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:18,560
Mom

2
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:21,040
You know how hard it was for Hongniang

3
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:22,359
to escape from Li Laosan.

4
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:23,799
Now you tell Li Laosan

5
00:01:23,799 --> 00:01:25,000
that Hongniang is at Changxian'er Temple.

6
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,599
Isn't that sending a sheep into a tiger's mouth?

7
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:27,519
Where she came from

8
00:01:27,519 --> 00:01:28,359
is where she must return.

9
00:01:28,439 --> 00:01:29,519
Such a slut,

10
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,079
better not let her ruin anyone else.

11
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:32,760
Didn't you say

12
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,560
if I just left her at Changxian Temple,

13
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:36,239
she would leave when I didn't show up?

14
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,640
What if she doesn't leave?

15
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,200
What if she comes back looking for you?

16
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:40,319
If she comes back for you,

17
00:01:40,319 --> 00:01:41,239
would you still want her?

18
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,319
But Mom...

19
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,519
No buts.

20
00:01:43,519 --> 00:01:44,280
Go back to your room and sleep.

21
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,280
Mom.

22
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:53,920
That child...

23
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:54,840
Sell her.

24
00:01:55,799 --> 00:01:57,480
The brat isn't yours anyway.

25
00:01:57,599 --> 00:01:58,400
Why keep her?

26
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:00,439
I understand, Mom.

27
00:02:01,239 --> 00:02:02,319
I'll listen to you.

28
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:23,759
Hongniang.

29
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,240
I swear,

30
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,280
I will protect you well.

31
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,840
I won't let you get hurt at all.

32
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,080
Hongniang.

33
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,280
Hongniang.

34
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:55,000
Mom.

35
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,000
Mom.

36
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:13,159
Mom.

37
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:16,759
Mom.

38
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:21,720
Mom.

39
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,439
Where are you?

40
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:28,959
Mom.

41
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,000
Mom.

42
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,360
Mom.

43
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,079
Mom.

44
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,600
My life is worthless anyway.

45
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,240
I should have died long ago.

46
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:13,040
If I hadn't fallen in love with you back then,

47
00:05:13,439 --> 00:05:14,639
and believed your promises,

48
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,759
I would have vanished from this world long ago.

49
00:05:19,759 --> 00:05:21,319
I was too naive.

50
00:05:21,839 --> 00:05:23,800
I thought if I gave the Zhang family an heir,

51
00:05:24,839 --> 00:05:25,920
we would be happy.

52
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,040
You love me,

53
00:05:32,959 --> 00:05:34,000
but you love your mother more.

54
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,160
You love yourself even more.

55
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,639
You killed my mom!

56
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,879
You killed my mom!

57
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:51,720
You killed my mom!

58
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:55,160
Let go of Sister Hong!

59
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:07,800
The time I spent with you

60
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:12,639
was the happiest time of my life.

61
00:06:40,399 --> 00:06:41,040
Sister Hong.

62
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:43,120
Are you okay?

63
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:44,839
Let's go home.

64
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:55,879
Let's go.

65
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,120
Let's go home.

66
00:07:02,759 --> 00:07:03,399
Hongniang.

67
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,560
Hongniang.

68
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:21,000
Everyone claims to love her,

69
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:23,160
but no one has ever truly considered her feelings.

70
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,519
It's truly ridiculous.

71
00:07:25,279 --> 00:07:27,199
Tell me, being liked by so many people at once,

72
00:07:27,319 --> 00:07:29,040
is it a good thing or a bad thing?

73
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:31,959
Everyone uses the legend of The Serpent's Wedding

74
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:33,360
to cover up their own crimes.

75
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,360
So this Serpent's Wedding

76
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:37,680
is nothing but a complete lie.

77
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:42,800
Then...

78
00:07:43,839 --> 00:07:45,160
your mother's passing

79
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,680
had nothing to do with the Long Snake.

80
00:07:50,319 --> 00:07:51,199
Tian'er.

81
00:07:58,839 --> 00:07:59,519
Mom.

82
00:08:00,279 --> 00:08:01,160
Tian'er.

83
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,199
Have you found me?

84
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,560
Mom.

85
00:08:21,199 --> 00:08:22,680
Mom.

86
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,039
Tian'er.

87
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:34,960
Run!

88
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,360
Get away from here!

89
00:08:43,639 --> 00:08:44,720
Run!

90
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:46,759
Mom.

91
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,159
Tian'er, run!

92
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:01,480
Leave me!

93
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,200
Mom!

94
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:05,720
Run!

95
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,600
Leave me!

96
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:09,240
Mom!

97
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,080
What's wrong?

98
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:18,919
For so many years...

99
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:21,120
I've been having a nightmare.

100
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:24,240
My mom is right in front of me.

101
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,360
I watch her helplessly

102
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,639
being taken away by Chang Xian'er.

103
00:09:29,559 --> 00:09:30,960
But I'm powerless.

104
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:36,240
Finding the truth behind The Serpent's Wedding all these years

105
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:39,080
has been my only goal.

106
00:09:41,879 --> 00:09:44,679
But now, The Serpent's Wedding doesn't exist at all.

107
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,120
Then my mom's death...

108
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:51,000
what is the truth exactly?

109
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,679
What have I been doing all these years?

110
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,399
Master.

111
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,559
I'm very worried about him.

112
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:19,240
Tian'er.

113
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:21,279
Mom has to go out for a bit.

114
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,360
I'll be back soon.

115
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,879
To make you noodles with tomato sauce.

116
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,080
Okay?

117
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:26,279
Okay.

118
00:11:26,279 --> 00:11:26,799
Mom.

119
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,200
Tian'er.

120
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,759
I'm back.
